<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤١١١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/598">إِسْحَاقُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2029">رَوْحٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6690">هِشَامٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5657">مُحَمَّدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4225">عَبِيدَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4500">عَلِيٍّ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ قَالَ يَوْمَ الْخَنْدَقِ: مَلَأَ اللهُ عَلَيْهِمْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١١١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بُيُوتَهُمْ وَقُبُورَهُمْ نَارًا، كَمَا شَغَلُونَا عَنْ صَلَاةِ الْوُسْطَى حَتَّى غَابَتِ الشَّمْسُ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>